title: Little Mix and 5 Seconds Of Summer set for Radio 1 Teen Awards - Prestwichandwhitefieldguide.co.uk
text:
A star-studded line-up including Little Mix and 5 Seconds Of Summer will help honour the UK's unsung teenage heroes at Radio 1's Teen Awards. Breakfast Show host Nick Grimshaw announced that Nick Jonas and All Time Low will also perform at the event, which will crown the year's best music, online, sport and entertainment stars, as voted by Radio 1 listeners.
